%div.row-fluid.space
  %div.span12
    %h2 What's next
    %p
      After installing the kit, check out the
      = link_to 'Rails Guides', 'http://guides.rubyonrails.org'
      for information about developing Ruby on Rails applications.
    %p
      Another great resource is the
      = link_to 'Ruby on Rails Tutorial', 'http://ruby.railstutorial.org'
      by Michael Hartl. While the tutorial is Mac-focused, it does provide
      great value and insight for Windows users as well. Additionally, there is
      about 15 hours of accompanying video to in case you're more visually-oriented.
    %p
      If you need assistance with RailsInstaller, please see our
      = link_to 'Google Group', 'http://groups.google.com/group/railsinstaller'
      where you can view posts from other users as well as ask questions. Any
      bugs with the installer should be reported on
      = link_to 'Github', 'http://github.com/railsinstaller'
      in the respective repositories (
      = link_to 'railsinstaller-windows', 'http://github.com/railsinstaller/railsinstaller-windows/issues'
      or
      = link_to 'railsinstaller-nix', 'http://github.com/railsinstaller/railsinstaller-nix/issues'
      ). There is also a
      = link_to '#railsinstaller', 'http://webchat.freenode.net/#railsinstaller'
      room on Freenode where you can get help in real-time chat.
